# --- Local-only artifacts (kept on disk, never pushed) ---
# System prompts: the third-party Antigravity (Google DeepMind) prompt and the
# Claude Code prompt — kept local, never redistributed.
*system_prompt*.md
# The Antigravity design prompt is injected via CLAUDE.md in the *_with_antigravity_prompt
# runs, so never publish ANY CLAUDE.md (global pattern survives folder renames).
**/CLAUDE.md
# Large screen recordings - kept local, not pushed
*.mp4
# SQLite runtime sidecar files (main *.sqlite/*.db already ignored)
*.sqlite-wal
*.sqlite-shm
*.db-wal
*.db-shm
*-journal
